  11764, 	"■Game.exe  Ver3.190\r\n  Fixed a bug where Data entries in Variable DB was automatically expanded when a \"Data Number\" greater than the current number of entries was read.\r\n  If you want to revert to the old behavior, set the version adjustment to \"Run as Old Ver3.18\" (the number of Data entries in Variable DB will automatically increase when read)."
