  11777, 	"■Game.exe  Ver3.233\r\n  [1] Fixed a bug where the map event was not erased when \"Erase Event\" was executed at the same time as page switching.\r\n  [2] Fixed a bug where the variable reference value was subtracted by 1 and the page number was added by 1 when a variable was specified for \"Page\" of \"Call Event\".\r\n  [3] Fixed a bug where the page of the map event did not switch until one frame had passed when \"Call Event\" was executed with page \"0\" immediately after switching to the run condition of another page.\r\n  If you want to revert to the old behavior around the page, set the version adjustment to \"Run as Old Ver3.21\"."
  11778, 	"■Game.exe  Ver3.250\r\n  In Move Route, the latest values of \"Map Self Variables\" and \"Normal Variables\" that can be changed during Move Route are now used.\r\n  If you want to revert to the old behavior, set the version adjustment to \"Run as Old Ver3.233\"."
