  12188, 	"■Game.exe  Ver3.566\r\n●When referencing Data by name in DB Management, the latest data name is now used for Variable DB.\r\n →  In the old behavior, the data name at the time of game startup is used.\r\n●Fixed a bug where character settings \"Hitbox ■\", \"Fixed Direction\", \"Pass-Through\", \"Above Hero\", \"Half-Tile Up/Left\", and \"Shadow Graphic\" reverted to the page defaults instead of the saved ones when the game was loaded.\r\n●Fixed a bug where strings such as \"\\\\self[0]\" (which should not be converted because it has two \\) were converted to numbers when processed by \"Remove Special Characters\" of Set String.\r\n●Fixed a bug where the Free Transform size was carried over when a Free Transform picture was erased over 0 frames and a normal picture was shown using the same ID."
